        "setup": "Authenticate the CLI by running `gel cloud login` as documented in [gel cloud login](https://docs.geldata.com/reference/using/cli/gel_cloud/gel_cloud_login). This signs you into Gel Cloud and stores a local access token for subsequent `gel cloud` commands.",
